**Year**: 2025

## üìù Project Description

RescueBot is a Wi-Fi-controlled robotic system designed to assist in hazardous 
environments where human presence is risky or impractical. The system features:

- Remote Wi-Fi control via web interface
- Autonomous obstacle avoidance
- Gas detection for hazardous environments  
- Human motion detection for search and rescue
- Emergency alert and communication systems
- Cost-effective design under ‚Çπ2000

